{"tid":1326353,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己好冇規紀律","createTime":"2019-07-17T07:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T11:54:27.000Z","uid":61394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ba5900f03490f1a1596fd885b6524361f04783","tid":1326353,"uid":61394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"大事就冇咩野 <br />\n一啲要好認真嘅野 都冇出現問題<br />\n<br />\n但小事就好大意<br />\n成日唔記得啲小事<br />\n或者係睇對方嘅態度做事<br />\n<br />\n例如話說今日要教班<br />\n點知自己都可以唔記得<br />\n(可能自己內心 對間野冇咩歸屬感  同埋間野又比唔到好多野我)<br />\n<br />\n但係教其他班 又冇呢啲情況出現<br />\n<br />\n求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99d9a94c73937c20439e5369e96e32c46016d79","tid":1326353,"uid":87799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:11:45.000Z","msg":"唔出事 冇麻煩到人咪得 唔洗樣樣野都咁完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23566718ed94f4ae7f88c3733ff531681987759d","tid":1326353,"uid":20584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:54:27.000Z","msg":"當差囉"}]}